        Default constructor.
        Parameters:
        actuatedIntake - The intake that raises and lowers with solenoids but doesn't move with the elevator.
        carriage - The intake mounted to the elevator, capable of detecting if it has the object to intake.
        elevator - The elevator that raises and lowers the carriage.
        intakeSolenoidPos - The position for the actuated intake to be at to intake game pieces.
        elevatorIntakePos - The position for the elevator to be at to intake game pieces. Defaults to 0.
        elevatorUpPos - The position for the elevator to be at to give the actuated intake enough clearance to move around.
        actuatedIntakeMode - The mode for the actuated intake to be in to intake game pieces.
        carriageIntakeMode - The mode for the carriage intake to be in to intake game pieces.
        carriageHoldMode - The mode for the carriage intake to be in to hold game pieces after intaking them. Defaults to off.
        raiseIntake - Whether to raise the intake after the condition is met. Defaults to false.
